DialogueText:
Patient:
I have a wet cough. Stuffy nose and sometimes get a headache. I took my temperature and it is normal but my cough is starting to get worse. Painful. Someone sneezed right next to me on 14 March.?
Doctor:
Symptoms. So you are worried that you might have Covid-19. You may also have common cold or influenza. Call hour General Physician. Report your symptoms. They will direct you to proper care.
